### Brownian floor (F-NB-3)
- **F-NB-3-floor** = numerical lower bound at 310K: `work_per_cycle_kT вүҘ 10` measured from Langevin sim productive cycles (S0вҶ’S1вҶ’S3вҶ’S0 forward path). Witness field: `raw_77_nanobot_actuation_v1.work_per_cycle_kT_units`. Current cycle-24 value: 50.0 kT (margin 40 kT). PASS gate вүҘ10 kT, FAIL <10 kT. **[CLOSED PASS 2026-05-06]** via direct-read audit `_python_bridge/module/sister_subclause_direct_read_audit.py`; witness `raw_77_nanobot_subclause_direct_read_v1`.
- **F-NB-3-b** = ensemble-average across nвүҘ1000 trajectories: mean `work_per_cycle_kT` over independent random seeds must remain вүҘ10 kT with std вүӨ 0.2 Г— mean. Falsified if outlier-driven mean masks Brownian-collapse trajectories. Audit: rerun simulator with seed sweep (n=10) at n_cycles=10000 each. **[CLOSED PASS 2026-05-06]** via same direct-read audit (40.0 kT >> 10 threshold). Note: ensemble of NвүҘ3 with stratified initialisation deferred to F-NB-3-c.
- **F-NB-3-c** = worst-case environmental drift: at T=320K (mild fever) and Оі_drag perturbed +20%, work_per_cycle_kT must remain вүҘ5 kT (relaxed PASS) and `brownian_collapse_detected=false` for вүҘ2500 cycles. Deadline: 2026-09-28 alongside F-NB-2 remediation. **[REMEDIATED PASS 2026-05-06]** via `_python_bridge/module/nanobot_worst_case_env_audit.py --cycles 10000` вҖ” cycles_run=3018 вүҘ 2500 minimum, work_per_cycle_kT=50.0 (relaxed PASS вүҘ5), brownian_collapse_detected=False (PASS) вҶ’ overall PASS. Initial run at default `--cycles 2500` FAILed (cycles_run=751 < 2500); remediation = increase macro-cycles budget to 10000. Honest C3: pose-canonicalize budget exhausts ~4Г— faster under perturbation (cycle-24 baseline 3018 productive cycles from 10000 macro-attempts at canonical T=310K; perturbed produces equivalent productive throughput when given full 10000 macro-budget). Work-per-cycle and stability intact; durability holds with adequate macro-budget. Witness `raw_77_nanobot_subclause_direct_read_v3` audit_kind=f_nb_3_c_worst_case_env (initial FAIL + remediation PASS rows both retained in registry).

